                  Server creation Express/Node JS

                                commands

                          1.create package.json ...... npm init
                                
                          2. Install Express........ npm i express

                          3. to run the server....... node index.js

                          4. to install nodemon...... npm i -g nodemon

                          5. install jsonwebtoken ...... npm i jsonwebtoken

                          6.install mongoose ........ npm i mongoose

                          7. install cors .......... npm i cors




                steps Server Creation

            1. Create a folder for Server

            2. Create package.json

            3. Install express

            4. create index.js file

            5. Import express in index.js

            6. create an application using express

            7. set up the port number 

            8. Resolve the http request from the client

            9. run the server

            10. parse json data in index.js

            11. Middlewares : (req,res,next)=>{}

                11.1 Application specific middlewares 

                11.2 Router specific middleware

            12. JWT token - to authenticate 

                12.1. Token generation  - sign()

                12.2.Token validation   - verify()

            13. Database connection

                13.1. install mongoose

                13.2. import mongoose

                13.3. define connection string

                13.4. create model

                13.5. export model
                
            14. Promise - to deal asynchronous events

                14.1. .then() - resolved state

                14.2.  catch() - reject state

            15. cors - cross origin resource sharing 
                        the protocol used to share data between 2 different port nmbers

                15.1. install cors

                15.2. import index.js

                15.3. using cors to specify the origin in server app